## Definition

+-- {: .un_defn}
###### Definition

For $X$ a [[scheme]], a set $\{p_i : U_i \to X\}$ of [[Ã©tale morphism]]s that [[cover]] $X$

$$
  X = \union_i p_i(U_i)
$$

(union of set-theoretical images) is an **Ã©tale cover** of $X$.

=--

The [[Ã©tale site]] has [[covering]]s given by the Ã©tale covers.

## Properties

+-- {: .un_prop}
###### Proposition

Every Ã©tale cover is a [[cover]] in the [[fpqc topology]].

=--

This appears for instance as ([de Jong, lemma 3.3](#deJong)).

